body: Hey, guys sorry, it's me again... Orz I'm learning "Outdoor_Microclimate_Map" and "Indoor_Microclimate_Map" right now and for indoor map every type runs quite well. But when I tried small highrises on "Outdoor_Microclimate_Map", the EP component shows error: 1. Solution exception:honeybee_DefaultScheduleLib And I didn't find the answer on google... So I upload my gh files here... Thank u for helping me ...
